content: व्याप्त {%<ab>p. p.</ab>%} {@--1@} Spread through, penetrated, pervaded, extended over, permeated, covered. {@--2@} Pervading, extending over all. {@--3@} Filled with, full of. {@--4@} Encompassed, surrounded. {@--5@} Placed, fixed. {@--6@} Obtained, possessed. {@--7@} Comprehended, included. {@--8@} Invariably accompanied (in logic); as in धूमो वह्निना व्याप्तः. {@--9@} Famous, celebrated. {@--10@} Expanded, stretched out.
